This is my first try with custom neon textures.
===============================================

_This map has 24CT's vs 24T's armed with an ak47. This game is all about skill and aim._

**Bloodxtype had made the base map: aim_colorbox_ak47_final, which I got permission from him and made a "Neon-Themed" edit of it.**

The map is quite simple and also- Short & Sweet.
